overview: Softeh Plus is a software development company based in Bucharest, Romania. The company’s mission is to transform each client into a trusting partner, and build solid business relationships, based on the most suitable software solutions than ensure customer’s accomplishment of business objectives. Softeh Plus is a Microsoft Certified Partner and Oracle Gold Partner company. We have and respect clear workflow procedures, that ensure a high and constant level of quality for our products and services. Having a consistent experience on the software development market in Romania and abroad, our team permanently strives to develop and maintain a very good relationship with it’s clients. We base our business relations on mutual trust and respect, and the basic principals we guide our activity by are: Fairness, Stability and Seriosity!
